  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>NEW EMPLOYEE RULES:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>TAKE A CLOSE LOOK AT YOUR SURROUNDINGS</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>IF YOU FIND ANOMALIES, TURN AROUND AND RUN</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>IF YOU DO NOT FIND ANOMALIES, DO NOT TURN BACK</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>-J JENKINS</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193800/extras/8f5df038a007f8220d8aab41f62be0e6.poster.avif?t=1761554088\" width=540 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193800/extras/8f5df038a007f8220d8aab41f62be0e6.webm?t=1761554088\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193800/extras/8f5df038a007f8220d8aab41f62be0e6.mp4?t=1761554088\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Description </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A short horror-themed walking simulator and memory game inspired by our memories of VHS stores and by similar anomaly games.  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Play Time </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1-4 hours</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Accessibility Options </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Camera Sensitivity </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Volume  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Language (UI only)</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Language Disclaimer </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Audio clips and Poster art are in English, but all of the anomalies are clearable without English.</p>",
